'''Alan Hiron''' is an [[United States|American]] [[Contract bridge|bridge]] player.

==Bridge accomplishments==

===Wins===

* [[World Senior Pairs Championship]] (1) 1990

* [[Gold Cup (bridge)|Gold Cup]] (1) 1963 <ref name="WBF Winners">[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (1)
** 0 (1) 1963 

===Runners-up===

* [[Gold Cup (bridge)|Gold Cup]] (1) 1974 <ref name="WBF Winners">[http://www.worldbridge.org/world-team-championships.aspx World Team Championship Winners]</ref>

* [[North American Bridge Championships]] (1)
** 0 (1) 1974 

